{"tid":2358394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《人民日報》揚言可將黎智英「送中」 鄧炳強: 香港和中國政府「兩方面都可以提出要求」","createTime":"2021-01-08T06:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T08:07:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b862157b0711b4a5b0679ea6128c6182244f3b50","tid":2358394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英就被指「勾結外國勢力」和「串謀欺詐」案件，正遭當局扣押。惟本港建制以至中國官媒《人民日報》曾揚言指稱國安公署可介入案件，令人關注黎智英會否被「送中」。警務處處長鄧炳強受訪指，香港本身已有法例可處理「港版國安法」案件，但同時稱如涉外國勢力複雜情況、香港無法自行處理，香港和中國政府「兩方面都可以提出要求」。<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長鄧炳強早前在建制媒體訪問，談及黎智英涉及「港版國安法」案件，認為香港本身已有法例可處理。但他同時引述「港版國安法」第55條，稱如涉及外國勢力複雜情況、香港無法自行處理就可提出由國家處理，國家亦可主動提出處理案件，「兩方面都可以提出要求」。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強在訪問中又指，至今仍然有人不斷測試法律底線，但指「港版國安法」對香港治安「起了正面作用」，目前社會上違反國家安全的行為已減少，如基本上已無人在街上高叫「香港獨立」，或者公然要求外國制裁香港。<br />\n<br />\n至於美國制裁令他的銀行服務和按揭受影響，但報道形容鄧「沒有甚麼感覺」。鄧又不點名批評美國亦曾制裁國際法庭人員，稱對其「霸權」和如何看待公義「沒有太大期望」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/KNND7LIOTVE7BKHKJWIPG2C2H4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FKNND7LIOTVE7BKHKJWIPG2C2H4%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=787f50d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FKNND7LIOTVE7BKHKJWIPG2C2H4%2F&h=dd1e4656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/KNND7LIOTVE7BKHKJWIPG2C2H4/</a>"},{"pid":"69ecd15ef96ad0eb1c68abbb68d89e7c21d68c2b","tid":2358394,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"黎智英當初決定留係香港真係要好大勇氣<br />\n佢上年即走 好似燒山咁過台灣 已經可以繼續正常生活<br />\n宜家當佢係黃絲最大大台咁搞<br />\n基本上唔送中都要坐到老<br />\n好多謝佢一路以黎無放棄過蘋果同繼續去外國游說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fdec60f951887d3da3bcaf26a5fc9d8b64b628e","tid":2358394,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb2fcdd7da54221902da6567b142b8b212d735f","tid":2358394,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"唔好吹 立即送佢去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地都捉左好多香港人去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想打仗就出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fbdadae7a4c19eca71c56fdee1eeacf431be6f","tid":2358394,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e571db9fee3ae58a4f99d1da92f83b3ab80e7368","tid":2358394,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"試緊美國新政府夠唔夠硬，<br />\n<br />\n人質外交2021"},{"pid":"8d938ec7d2d2460f1dbe5b9aef2eb528eb5656b1","tid":2358394,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:07:09.000Z","msg":"我仲似為係老納post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}